nl_problem:
# Task: Multi-Constraint Check (Density 20)
# Interface:
Class: Solution
Method: isValid(self, n: int) -> bool

# Objective:
Return True if the integer `n` satisfies ALL of the following 20 independent constraints:
1. n is greater than 2
2. n is not equal to 104
3. n is a multiple of 1
4. n is greater than 8
5. n is not equal to 110
6. n is a multiple of 2
7. n is greater than 14
8. n is not equal to 116
9. n is a multiple of 4
10. n is greater than 20
11. n is not equal to 122
12. n is a multiple of 5
13. n is greater than 26
14. n is not equal to 128
15. n is a multiple of 7
16. n is greater than 32
17. n is not equal to 134
18. n is a multiple of 8
19. n is greater than 38
20. n is not equal to 140

  (name "isValid")

  (constraints
    (constraint "n is greater than 2")

    (constraint "n is greater than 8")
    (constraint "n is not equal to 110")
    (constraint "n is a multiple of 2")
    (constraint "n is greater than 14")

    (constraint "n is not equal to 128")
    (constraint "n is a multiple of 7")

    (constraint "n is not equal to 134")
    (constraint "n is a multiple of 8")
    (constraint "n is greater than 38")
    (constraint "n is not equal to 140")
  )
  (goal
    (description "Return True if n satisfies all 20 constraints.")
    (rule "Apply each constraint in sequence.")
    (return "True if all constraints are satisfied, False otherwise.")
  )
)
